00:31:43.600 --> 00:31:46.250
For instance, I
would do some of what

00:31:46.250 --> 00:31:49.850
I call heart practices, loving
kindness, or compassion.

00:31:49.850 --> 00:31:51.690
And for the first
couple of years

00:31:51.690 --> 00:31:53.760
that I would do those
kind of practices,

00:31:53.760 --> 00:31:56.270
I didn't even mean it at all.

00:31:56.270 --> 00:31:57.730
[LAUGHTER]

00:31:57.730 --> 00:32:01.760
Like I would say to myself,
