00:32:41.780 --> 00:32:45.650
I'm not judging my own inner
meditation voice so much

00:32:45.650 --> 00:32:47.090
anymore.

00:32:47.090 --> 00:32:50.000
10 years of just really
gradually looking back

00:32:50.000 --> 00:32:51.085
how it worked slowly.

00:32:54.230 --> 00:32:57.740
