meditative phenomena

00:33:24.190 --> 00:33:28.360
can happen when you're
practicing all day, every day

00:33:28.360 --> 00:33:31.980
for weeks or months on end.

00:33:31.980 --> 00:33:35.370
But my teachers were always
very-- a little bit dismissive

00:33:35.370 --> 00:33:37.561
of that phenomenon.

00:33:37.561 --> 00:33:39.560
They were a little bit
like, oh yeah, that's OK.

00:33:39.560 --> 00:33:41.960
