can you pay attention to that?

00:33:49.480 --> 00:33:50.320
Can you note that?

00:33:50.320 --> 00:33:53.080
Is it pleasant or unpleasant?

00:33:53.080 --> 00:33:54.610
Are you clinging to it?

00:33:54.610 --> 00:33:56.220
Rather than putting
much emphasis

00:33:56.220 --> 00:33:59.990
on those big
meditation phenomenon,

00:33:59.990 --> 00:34:01.111
