00:34:01.111 --> 00:34:02.860
Pay attention to it
like you pay attention

00:34:02.860 --> 00:34:05.240
to the breath or the
motions or the mind.

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:08.949
You don't have to push it away,
but don't get attached to it.

00:34:08.949 --> 00:34:11.840
Don't think that that's
like the real thing.

00:34:11.840 --> 00:34:14.429
Just part of what happens.

00:34:14.429 --> 00:34:17.630
